location.fullValue: Ridgeview Plan, Vail Parke at Rocking K

data.description: PREMIUM LOT on cul-de-sac which boasts stellar mountain and sunset views. Don't miss out on this 2.75% assumable VA Loan.  Beautiful 4-bedroom 3-full bath Pulte built, single story home in Rocking K. Enjoy all the benefits of a new build home without the extra costs for backyard landscaping, custom gray interior paint throughout, reverse osmosis, water softener system and solar screens on all windows. Chef's kitchen has a gas stove, large island with built in sink and large pantry. Flex room with custom barndoors can be used for home office or child's play space. The x-large Primary Suite with barndoor access to adjoining bathroom features glass enclosed rain shower, large double vanity, and walk-in closet.  Award winning Vail School district! **Seller has an assumable VA Loan at 2.75% interest rate for VA Eligible buyers**
